Session management
Parameters management
Sensible input format
Job control
Database internals
Analysis registration
Slicing/summary table

###
Definitions
    session = single mechanism used on a set of models + experiments + parameters
        e.g. a big mesh run on a model/expt for visualization
    * parameter set = collection of parameters needed to run a stage
        e.g. simulation parameter set, or analysis parameter set
    run = multiple simulations of a model + experiment with a single parameter set

###
Goals
    run on a mesh -> visualize slices
    global fit to loads of data
        wtf visualization can i do?
            run 1d slice meshes afterwards for visualization?
